Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.00,0:00:21.32,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}掌上的微风 在光芒中一闪一闪地舞动
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.35,0:00:35.21,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}我已经能用全新的笑容 向陌生人道早安
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:47.43,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}尽管回忆溢满心头 我的朝气绝不认输
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.46,0:00:57.27,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无所谓在干掉的泪痕中 有一扇通往梦想的门
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.30,0:01:01.28,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}如果烦恼就无法前进
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.31,0:01:10.03,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}没错 我会以迎接朋友的方式 温柔地微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.06,0:01:14.79,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.82,0:01:23.88,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}无意间悲伤虽然涌上心头 我也会试着与人和好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.91,0:01:27.80,OPC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx80\3c&HFFFFFF&}因为这是我们的约定
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.78,0:01:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.53,0:01:44.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也快结束了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.77,0:01:49.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来啊来啊,快来买 太太,喜欢就算你便宜
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.97,0:01:53.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,南北货都有喔 快啊快啊,快来买
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.31,0:01:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗨,勤奋学生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.85,0:01:59.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这回换在荞麦面店打工吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.15,0:02:02.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,大婶要不要买 明天要吃的过年荞麦面?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.65,0:02:06.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,不用了 我们明天就回乡下老家过年了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.46,0:02:09.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,倒是你要怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.29,0:02:12.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我想大年初一晚上回去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.83,0:02:19.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是个不孝子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在过年前回去啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.24,0:02:25.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这也没办法啊 我得拿到打工钱才回得去
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:28.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,车钱不是家里寄来给你了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.25,0:02:31.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已经用光了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.15,0:02:33.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有同情的余地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:36.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四谷,你别忙着数落我 你自己怎么样?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.52,0:02:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有地方回去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.42,0:02:42.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且也请假了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.23,0:02:44.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你一年到头都在休假不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.90,0:02:47.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是在做什么工作啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.17,0:02:49.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不告诉你们
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过说真的,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.22,0:03:09.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这间脏兮兮的房间里过年 真的太凄惨了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.72,0:03:11.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要你管!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.29,0:03:13.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊,连个电视都没有
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.99,0:03:16.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且一定冷得半死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.93,0:03:20.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除夕夜的孤独 是特别难熬的唷
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.97,0:03:22.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:27.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很冷清喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.47,0:03:32.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很难过喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.91,0:03:35.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美 你也不抬乡下过年不是吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.38,0:03:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什么资格取笑我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.45,0:03:40.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.42,0:03:43.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人家我要跟管理员 在管理室里看电视
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.62,0:03:47.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟管理员?好好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.36,0:03:49.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很羡慕吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.36,0:03:53.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好羡慕喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.80,0:03:56.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我好寂寞喔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.17,0:03:57.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要不要也一起来?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.33,0:03:58.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人多比较热闹嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.87,0:04:01.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.04,0:04:10.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,#19 五代和响子! 俩人的夜晚充满危险
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.39,0:04:15.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.49,0:04:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然可以 人多热闹比较好玩
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去打工罗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.33,0:04:24.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,请加油喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.43,0:04:26.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,九点左右,我会拿荞麦面回来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.53,0:04:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为我在荞麦面店打工
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.03,0:04:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赚到一顿过年荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.37,0:04:31.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.47,0:04:33.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们一起走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.41,0:04:41.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,我走了 祝你新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.85,0:04:43.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.99,0:04:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他要回哪里去呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.72,0:04:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.35,0:05:16.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我回乡下过年罗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.51,0:05:18.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,大年初四回来是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.58,0:05:21.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,不用送了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.29,0:05:22.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.15,0:05:23.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.66,0:05:31.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸,你快点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.61,0:06:19.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一郎,今年也平安地渡过了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.18,0:06:21.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今后也请继续保佑我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.88,0:06:26.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.85,0:06:30.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,这里是一刻馆
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.09,0:06:33.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在,请您稍等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.60,0:06:39.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.77,0:06:47.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,是我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:49.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦,滑雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.77,0:06:51.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.31,0:06:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,六点钟在上野车站 中央剪票口集合?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.78,0:06:57.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.55,0:06:58.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候见罗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.52,0:07:07.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.01,0:07:25.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要去滑雪?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.44,0:07:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊,跟朋友一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.38,0:07:29.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过好像不太好喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:31.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该怎么说呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.45,0:07:34.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让你跟五代 两个人独处好像有点…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.62,0:07:39.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到时候喊破嗓子也没人来救你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.29,0:07:43.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看我还是不要去滑雪好了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.13,0:07:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.26,0:07:49.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很想去滑雪吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.87,0:07:51.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想是想啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.54,0:07:52.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.94,0:07:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.97,0:07:56.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会有事的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.21,0:07:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这关系到贞操危机喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.37,0:08:00.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦,你想太多了啦,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.44,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不要紧吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:05.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们要更相信五代才对
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.55,0:08:06.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说得也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.75,0:08:08.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.95,0:08:10.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我得快点准备出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.90,0:08:28.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总…惣一郎,你一定要保佑我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.02,0:08:40.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员,那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.52,0:08:43.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,慢走,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.53,0:08:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会买土产回来给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.76,0:08:53.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.13,0:09:56.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干嘛啊!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.18,0:10:14.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.65,0:10:20.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,总之,只能努力 不要让气氛变得很诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.33,0:10:32.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,管理员
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.97,0:10:39.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没有跟朱美一起来洗吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.10,0:10:43.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美不在的事应该跟他说吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.98,0:10:51.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,香皂的味道好香喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.02,0:10:53.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为刚洗完澡嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.48,0:10:55.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么我待会去找你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.25,0:10:57.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,待会见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.69,0:11:03.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会不会想太多了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.53,0:11:09.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚洗好的头好诱人喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.20,0:11:13.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这时候如果能俩人独处 那就棒透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.31,0:11:23.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要从今年喝到明年
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.05,0:11:26.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来来,尽管喝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.32,0:11:30.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大姊,你真是好酒量啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.02,0:11:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今晚心情真好,我要喝到爽
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.39,0:11:35.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:46.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧,碍事者不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.21,0:11:51.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我早料到会有这种事 已经先去洗过澡了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.31,0:11:52.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响子,真的可以吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.01,0:11:54.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.42,0:12:00.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他在干嘛? 怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.40,0:12:00.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.42,0:12:30.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请进
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.52,0:12:32.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,欢迎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.79,0:12:33.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打扰了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.46,0:12:37.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是三人份的过年荞麦面
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.80,0:12:39.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.20,0:12:40.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有这个
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.10,0:12:43.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美过年时不可能不喝酒吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.27,0:12:46.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.20,0:12:49.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要喝咖啡?还是茶?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.44,0:12:50.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.11,0:12:51.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.68,0:12:53.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美人呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.91,0:12:55.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,砂糖要放几匙?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.58,0:12:57.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,麻烦给我一匙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.09,0:13:02.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请问…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.12,0:13:04.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.76,0:13:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.56,0:13:09.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对了…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.99,0:13:12.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我都忘了,还要放奶精才行
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.63,0:13:14.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要放奶精?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.10,0:13:17.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用了,倒是…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.07,0:13:19.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.34,0:13:24.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了,来了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:27.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,哪位?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.68,0:13:28.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,朱美
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.05,0:13:31.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我现在到旅馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.32,0:13:33.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代在那里吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.18,0:13:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.59,0:13:36.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他来听一下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.79,0:13:40.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要叮咛他,绝对不能想入非非
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.49,0:13:45.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没…没有这个必要,真的没事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:47.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.16,0:13:50.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过万一出事的话 一定要放声大叫喔,知道吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.70,0:13:53.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会啦,不可以怀疑他
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.57,0:13:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你要小心点啦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:56.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我会的,再见
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.27,0:14:00.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要相信他才行
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.47,0:14:03.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美说她已经平安到旅馆了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.54,0:14:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么!旅馆?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:08.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她去滑雪啊,她没跟你说吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:14.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是第一次听到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.25,0:14:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.22,0:14:18.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还以为她跟你说了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.96,0:14:21.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.36,0:14:23.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.16,0:14:28.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱美不在家啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.43,0:14:29.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.60,0:14:35.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩我们两个人 真的好冷清喔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.84,0:14:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.57,0:15:10.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有两个人的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.55,0:15:17.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大好机会
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.88,0:15:21.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在无论怎么大哭大叫 都不会有人来打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.00,0:15:34.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,这个橘子我吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.60,0:15:35.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请吃
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.64,0:15:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电视真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.81,0:15:47.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不打算买吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.48,0:15:51.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 以前因为怕影响考大学没有买
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.45,0:15:53.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过现在靠打工费买一台好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.18,0:15:55.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有电视还是比较有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.79,0:15:56.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.79,0:16:03.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才不管什么电视不电视
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.03,0:16:05.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从下面伸手过去握住她的手
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.34,0:16:19.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,我都忘了 我把煎饼放在暖桌下面
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.22,0:16:28.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样可以除掉一些湿气 吃起来比较香脆
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.45,0:16:29.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原来如此
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.73,0:16:39.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,既然这样就一股作气…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.70,0:16:42.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,声音会不会太小声了?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.01,0:16:48.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一…一股作气…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.88,0:16:52.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把她推倒…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.37,0:17:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.20,0:17:17.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.61,0:17:27.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊,对了,吃煎饼要喝茶才对
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.55,0:17:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,我的嘴巴也蛮干的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.12,0:17:36.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请喝茶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.45,0:18:03.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 差不多该去准备荞麦面了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.82,0:18:05.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也来帮忙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.75,0:18:07.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在那里看电视就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.42,0:18:15.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是,我来这里打扰你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.23,0:18:19.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么介意
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.40,0:18:21.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.44,0:18:34.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么,面碗…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.91,0:18:36.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.25,0:18:37.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我拿出来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.38,0:18:38.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.02,0:18:43.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请拿面碗来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:44.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:50.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来了,这个时候会是谁啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.53,0:18:53.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂,哪位?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.00,0:18:55.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀,是一之濑太太啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.04,0:18:58.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瓦斯的总开关?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.34,0:19:00.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我知道了,我去看一下
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.94,0:19:02.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我挂了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.74,0:19:07.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去一号房看看
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:07.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.42,0:19:21.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,只差一步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.54,0:19:32.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:41.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只剩…只剩一步而已
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.75,0:19:50.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶,我好想做喔!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.01,0:20:15.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请…请问你听到什么了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.08,0:20:17.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,听到一点点
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:24.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有啦,我只是想去滑雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.52,0:20:26.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很羡慕朱美能去滑雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.33,0:20:29.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,滑雪
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.49,0:20:31.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的,我误会了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.50,0:20:42.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也留下了很多回忆 又到了年终
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.01,0:20:45.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.28,0:20:47.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多该走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.11,0:20:48.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么快就要走了?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.31,0:20:51.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊,荞麦面也吃了 那我走了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.48,0:20:52.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新年快乐
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.52,0:20:58.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怀着怎么样的心情 聆听除夕的钟声呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.70,0:21:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他没有对我做任何不规矩的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.46,0:21:08.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代真是个绅士啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.44,0:21:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太没用了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.99,0:21:37.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕,我想起来了…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.58,0:21:59.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不应该怀疑他的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.99,0:22:04.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错,五代不是那种人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.67,0:22:21.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个千载难逢的机会
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.77,0:22:23.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我居然败给了压力
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.54,0:22:26.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,决定了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.98,0:22:28.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要去邀请他
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.15,0:22:31.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我应该一口气推倒她
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.52,0:22:41.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五代,五代
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:42.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还醒着吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.00,0:22:46.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,响…响子?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.60,0:22:54.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在开门的那一瞬间
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.21,0:22:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我期待她穿着透明睡衣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.32,0:23:09.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不要一起去参加跨年参拜?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.39,0:23:13.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好,我陪你一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.76,0:23:17.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是响子不是那种女人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.60,0:23:22.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年也请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我才要请你多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.74,0:23:27.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年你要许什么愿望呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.17,0:23:30.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个嘛 希望今年也是个美好的一年
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.78,0:23:32.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.62,0:23:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年我一定要推倒你
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:43.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.73,0:23:52.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故乡应该是在很远的 令人用来怀念的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.20,0:23:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是回到故乡的五代 却好像不是这样
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.13,0:23:57.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别以为5号房永远都在
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.57,0:23:58.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,相聚一刻下一回
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.20,0:24:01.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“响子焦虑不安? 五代迟迟未归之谜”
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.54,0:24:06.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老实说,你不在身边 我就无法展现笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.57,0:24:06.57,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.17,0:24:34.52,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}那天在陌生的城市下了一场阵雨
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.55,0:24:41.24,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你非常在意淋湿的高跟鞋
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.27,0:24:49.45,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}从前你用那隐藏着 稚气的侧脸和我交谈
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.48,0:24:55.54,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你说的话语至今仍能想起
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.57,0:25:03.34,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}一开始就仿佛 置身电影中的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.37,0:25:12.02,EDC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx90}你轻声细语地说着 安静的最后一幕

